Sample Data Engineering Notes for RAG Pipeline

Apache Spark
Apache Spark is a distributed data processing engine used for large-scale ETL, analytics, and
streaming workloads.

Apache Kafka
Kafka is a distributed event streaming platform used for real-time pipelines and messaging.

Apache Airflow
Airflow orchestrates workflows using DAGs and schedules ETL pipelines.

Apache Iceberg
Iceberg is a table format supporting schema evolution, ACID transactions, snapshots, and time
travel.

Data Engineering Skills
Important skills include Python, SQL, Spark, Kafka, Airflow, cloud platforms, and data modeling.
